@startuml
title 打开相机并实时预览 - 时序图

actor "操作者" as User
participant "MainWindow / CameraPanel" as UI
participant "CameraController" as CameraController
participant "MUCamCameraDriver" as Driver
participant "ObservationSession" as Session
participant "ImageViewport" as Viewport

User -> UI: 点击 Refresh
UI -> CameraController: refreshDevices()
CameraController -> Driver: enumerateDevices()
Driver --> CameraController: CameraDevice 列表
CameraController --> UI: 显示设备列表

User -> UI: 选择设备并点击 Open
UI -> CameraController: open(deviceId)
CameraController -> Driver: open(deviceId)
Driver --> CameraController: open ok
UI -> Session: start()

loop preview running
  Session -> CameraController: requestFrame()
  CameraController -> Driver: getFrame()
  Driver --> CameraController: ImageFrame
  CameraController --> Session: ImageFrame
  Session -> Viewport: setFrame(frame)
  Viewport -> Viewport: paint frame + overlay
end

@enduml

